data.description: One of a kind and almost impossible to find All Steel Frame Residential Home in Jacksonville. Yes, Steel Frame! Brand new construction 3BR/2BA with 2 car garage is ready for new owner. Open floor plan with kitchen overlooking large family room. Kitchen has island, granite countertops, SS appliances, recessed lighting and prewired for pendant lights. Vinyl plank flooring throughout entry way, hall, family room, kitchen, laundry room and baths. Master bath includes walk in tile shower and vanity with dual sinks and granite countertops. Guest bathroom has tile shower with tub. *** This home qualifies for special financing. 3% in down payment assistance that is forgiven after 5 years ***  2-10 home warranty included. Pictures are of completed home. 3-D Virtual Tour walk through available.
